  "name": "Lucid Dreamer (Varisian Wanderers, Wonderseekers)",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/sundries/books/book-embossed-jewel-gold-purple.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Your dreams are a special place of power that only you get to enjoy; driving away threats to your subconscious is as easy as slamming a door.</p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl65_LabelType\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl65_LabelType\">Varisian Wanderers, Wonderseekers</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p>You receive a +1 trait bonus on Knowledge (planes) checks and a +2 trait bonus on Will saves against effects on your dreaming mind or subconscious, such as a night hag's dream haunting ability, the nightmare spell, and illusions of the phantasm subschool.</p>",
